longBusinessSummary: G2 Goldfields Inc. focuses on acquisition and exploration of gold deposits in Guiana. It holds interests in properties located at Oko Aremu and Puruni districts in Guiana. It also holds interest in the Sandy Lake project in the Sandy Lake Archean Greenstone Belt, Canada. The company was formerly known as Sandy Lake Gold Inc. and changed its name to G2 Goldfields Inc. in April 2019. G2 Goldfields Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
